title: Not Right Now
description:
After reviewing the audio from an interview with an expert for The Case, Mike delivers his ruling (00:01:20). On the fourth anniversary of Sensitivity Training, Kirk looks back by reaching out to many of the individuals involved (00:52:48). KFC Radio leads us to the new Barstool company values (00:07:00). Rico Bosco is back from his break but it seems his made man status is in jeopardy (00:25:09). There's nothing funny about Greg Gutfeld as Michelle Tafoya makes her first political appearance after leaving the sports broadcasting world (00:40:00). The toughest part of Chris' movie endeavor, calls & more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
